2012-04-17  Aric Stewart  <aric@codeweavers.com>

	Copy getopt.h from old common/win/my_getopt-1.5/my_getopt
	This patch completes the copy from
	4d8f39020ac83602c1647d4af04e8b19bf74ed6e which missed this file.

